Package ClientSide.client

'client' package contains the application entry point, and some functionalities like configuration and connectivity.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Client.ClientStatusHandler
    ClientStatusHandler: handler interface for updating the UI according to the connection status of the client.
    Client.MessageReceiveHandler
    MessageReceiveHandler: Handler interface for message from the server to display on UI.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Client
    Client: Implementation of AbstractClient that can receive and send Message type message.
    ClientConfiguration
    ClientConfiguration: POJO to client application configuration.
    ClientEntryPoint
    EntryPoint: The entry point of the application.

Package ClientSide.client Description

'client' package contains the application entry point, and some functionalities like configuration and connectivity.

'Client' project contains all the functionality of the client side.
